{"tid":2212082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★突發！滙豐倫敦股價折合跌穿29港元","createTime":"2020-09-21T13:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T08:50:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d497ddea8e11e3fd1e19200ab878e8e77dd43000","tid":2212082,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"滙豐控股(00005)倫敦股價報288.45便士，挫逾5%；折合報28.71港元，較港股收市再跌2.01%。<br />\n滙控股價不濟，帶領全線銀行股偏軟，亦令歐洲股市出現7月30日以來最大跌幅。目前英國富時100指數下跌2.6%，除了滙控因素外，也受到英國旅遊股下跌的打擊，英國政府料將被告知該國正處於疫情大流行的「關鍵時刻」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200921/bkn-20200921173948996-0921_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200921%2Fbkn-20200921173948996-0921_00842_001.html&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=cefc450c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200921/bkn-20200921173948996-0921_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e80078c34f0e4e217d698cb71002bfe3558f620e","tid":2212082,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd0b4207beb789a2cf22448563e2435ebd4e2aa","tid":2212082,"uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jebywfx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJebywfx.gif&h=b96103bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae7a90a40324a0f68f2459e9ab1cbe07b8e92d83","tid":2212082,"uid":2054,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"凍結星火7千萬 簽名撐國安法<br />\n報應呀<i